id: pm-6zqq
title: Hybrid semantic reindex should emit bounded progress and deterministic JSON completion
description: "During 2026-05-10 audit, pm reindex --mode hybrid --json against 685 items drove local qwen3 Ollama embeddings for over ten minutes and exited without a JSON result payload in the agent session, while hybrid search and health vectorization remained usable. Reindex needs bounded agent-facing progress, resumability/cancellation clarity, and deterministic completion output for long embedding runs."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 0
tags[1]: pm-cli
created_at: "2026-05-10T22:12:09.922Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-10T22:12:26.396Z"
author: opencode-agent
acceptance_criteria: "Hybrid semantic reindex reports deterministic progress/noninteractive heartbeat, exits with JSON success or structured failure, and documents expected local-embedding runtime/resume behavior."
parent: pm-rnpb
